	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Right.
<br />Overall, 111 will be 8 pixels back, 112 5 pixels back, 113 2 pixels back, 114 1 pixel forwad, 115 4 pixels forwad, 116 7 pixels forwad, etc...
<br />The whole thing should be rewritten with different timed cycles for PAL format, and probably other beams are possible.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
